{"tid":854466,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封殺港獨】不滿港府拒續發簽證 《金融時報》為馬凱提上訴","createTime":"2018-10-09T11:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T13:36:47.000Z","uid":47272,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"114cc00bcac99a5052af5e8cf019802de0b4cbda","tid":854466,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181009&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58774370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181009%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58774370&d=MUqSzCzHwhhixO6PguiJ4YM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=b5c0117b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181009%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58774370&h=e22567d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181009&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58774370</a><br />\n特區政府至今未就拒絕向任職《金融時報》的馬凱續發工作簽證一事作出解釋，特首林鄭月娥堅持有關出入境政策，按國際慣例一般不會公開。《金融時報》今天回覆《蘋果》查詢馬凱會否提出上訴時表明，由於香港當局沒有提供解釋，回應為何馬凱不獲續發工作簽證，《金融時報》即將就此事提出上訴，有關上訴將會直接向香港入境處提出（In the absence of an explanation from the Hong Kong authorities, the FT is appealing the recent rejection of a renewed work visa for Victor Mallet. The FT is appealing the visa rejection to the HK Immigration Department）<br />\n大律師公會憲制及人權事務委員會主席布穎琪今日則在《南華早報》撰文，指現時未有一個解釋拒絕續批簽證給馬凱的原因，令人信服的推論是因為馬凱早前以外國記者會的身份，籌辦香港民族黨召集人陳浩天的演講。但文章指演講發生在保安局局長取締民族黨之前，而相關決定被質疑是否合法和與《基本法》保障人權的條文相符，保安局局長至今也沒有提供任何民族黨會使用暴力的理據：「如果取締民族黨本身是不合法，那麼拒逐馬凱便會加倍荒謬。（If the ban itself is unlawful, it renders the eviction of Mallet doubly absurd.）」<br />\n布穎琪並稱，行會召集人（陳智思）曾指入境處毋須解釋為何拒發簽證，但馬凱若根據《入境條例》提出反對，特首會同行會便要考慮其反對，並確認或變更有關拒批簽證的決定，屆時便是特首林鄭月娥就她的決定，提出解釋原因的時候。《蘋果》今午曾向馬凱查詢會否提出反對，他指不知道會否提出，而他今早則在Facebook感謝香港人聯署聲援他，至今要求政府解釋聯署人數已過2萬。"},{"pid":"1d6251720dbb854a720015e0a8c88450a37d9066","tid":854466,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96c0e87f23def7ea85079d72a3ded226cfc86ba","tid":854466,"uid":58031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:28:07.000Z","msg":"搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ace347e4059657582d8812eb3ba3c6a10139e2","tid":854466,"uid":8858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"有花生食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b045494b3cb2d40fe26dae94ad8c94a5dbe2e36f","tid":854466,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9412a5ac5343e1b91bcc6cf91051f90df7913db7","tid":854466,"uid":156611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:33:04.000Z","msg":"仲有無得聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22258845225c5acdbd69adb594f9509638114d86","tid":854466,"uid":82935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就馬凱事件.<br />\n強力譴責 英美 干涉 港共內政.<br />\n要求 英國政府 以 &quot;國際慣例&quot; 做法<br />\n歸還 爱国爱党 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">賣香港</span> 既 <br />\n特首林鄭月娥及梁振英一家大細 中国人身份."},{"pid":"be99448be9854b7c4fe0559b7db18e8d40125bc3","tid":854466,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍未到支那先到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a655bb7f1155b5d89896e201ad6a01f6a6e628f0","tid":854466,"uid":15730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9412a5ac5343e1b91bcc6cf91051f90df7913db7","tid":854466,"uid":156611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:33:04.000Z","msg":"仲有無得